**Borderline eligible?** If you currently use a competitor (Rippling, Remote, Gusto) and are considering switching, signing up through SaaSOffers qualifies you as a new customer. The 3-month minimum is standard across Deel's startup program — if you're seriously hiring internationally, 3 months is barely enough time to onboard your first few workers anyway.

## How to Claim This Deal Step by Step

