|---|---|
| Contractor management | $49/contractor/month |
| EOR employment | From $599/employee/month |
| Global payroll (own entity) | From $29/employee/month |

For a startup with 3 international contractors, that's $147/month or **$1,764/year** just in platform fees — before any EOR services. Your $1,500 in credits covers nearly a full year of those fees.

