## What Is Pipedrive?

Pipedrive is the CRM built by salespeople, for salespeople. While most CRMs are designed to generate reports for managers, Pipedrive is designed to help the person doing the actual selling close more deals with less administrative overhead. The visual pipeline is the center of the experience — you see every deal, at every stage, at a glance.

Founded in 2010 and used by over 100,000 companies, Pipedrive has become one of the most popular CRM choices for startups and SMBs in 2026. The product is particularly strong for teams doing outbound sales, where tracking follow-ups and activity sequences across dozens of open deals would otherwise fall through the cracks.

For a startup doing founder-led sales, Pipedrive is one of the best first CRM choices. It requires virtually no configuration to get started, connects to Gmail or Outlook in minutes, and surfaces the exact information you need before every customer call — without requiring a Salesforce admin to set it up.

