Pipedrive's pipeline view shows every active deal as a card in a Kanban-style board. You see which stage each deal is in, when the last activity was, and what the next action is — all without clicking into individual records. For a founder managing 20–40 open opportunities, this visual overview prevents deals from going cold simply because they fell off your radar.

