When you ship a new onboarding flow, a redesigned pricing page, or a changed feature UI, Mixpanel lets you measure the behavioral impact. Compare conversion rates, retention, and feature adoption between users who experienced different variants. This closes the loop between product changes and business outcomes in a way that gut feel never can.

