## What Is Ahrefs?

Ahrefs is one of the most powerful SEO toolsets in the world, used by over 7 million marketers, SEO professionals, and content teams to understand search rankings, analyze competitor strategies, track backlinks, and identify content opportunities. The platform crawls over 8 billion web pages per day — one of the largest web crawl operations outside of Google — and turns that data into actionable SEO intelligence.

Ahrefs Webmaster Tools (AWT) is the free tier of Ahrefs that focuses specifically on your own website. Where the paid Ahrefs plans let you research any website or keyword in the world, AWT gives you full visibility into your own domain's SEO health, backlink profile, and organic keyword performance — completely free, forever.

In 2026, organic search is one of the highest-ROI acquisition channels available to startups. A company that ranks on the first page of Google for 20–30 high-intent keywords can generate hundreds of qualified leads per month with no ongoing paid media cost. Ahrefs Webmaster Tools is the foundation you need to build and monitor that organic presence — and it costs nothing.

## Why This Deal Matters for Startups

The financial value of Ahrefs Webmaster Tools is simple: a full Ahrefs subscription starts at $99/month. AWT gives you a meaningful subset of that functionality — site audit, backlink monitoring, keyword tracking, and content performance data — completely free, with no time limit.

For a startup in its first 1–2 years, AWT covers most of what you actually need. You're not yet doing deep competitor research or hunting for keyword opportunities across thousands of domains. You're fixing technical SEO issues on your own site, monitoring whether your content is earning backlinks, and tracking whether your target keywords are moving up in rankings. AWT handles all of that.

**The compounding math of SEO in 2026:** A startup that starts fixing technical SEO issues, earning backlinks, and publishing optimized content in month 1 builds an organic traffic base that grows month over month. A startup that starts in month 12 has lost 12 months of compounding. AWT makes it free and easy to start immediately.

## What's Included in the Deal

- **Ahrefs Webmaster Tools — completely free forever** (no trial, no expiry, no payment method required)
- **Full site audit** — 100+ technical SEO checks including crawl errors, broken links, missing meta tags, slow pages, and Core Web Vitals issues
- **Backlink monitoring** — see every website linking to yours, with new and lost link alerts
- **Organic keyword tracking** — see which keywords your site ranks for and your position history
- **Content performance data** — identify your top-performing pages by organic traffic
