- AWT only shows data for websites you own and verify

## Eligibility Requirements

- **No requirements** — Ahrefs Webmaster Tools is available to any website owner for free
- No funding stage, company age, or revenue requirements
- Simply verify ownership of your website to activate (via DNS record, HTML tag, or Google Search Console)
